extendedInfo.description: Fancy JigSaw is a classic puzzle game. Drag the Pet dog pieces to the right place to re-establish the full picture. Don't sweat it if you are unable to solve the puzzle easily. You can use the peek button to preview the original image.There are 100 levels in this game. The further you advance, the more challenging the puzzle becomes. This app also allows you to save the Pet dog images to your SD .These amazing jigsaw puzzles contain a large number of high quality images of Pet dog in different parts of the World.In Jigsaw Puzzles "Pet dog" we present high quality images withdifferent kinds of dog,Cute Doggie, Retrievers ,bull-dog ,Malamute , shepherd dog , hunterâ¦â¦ Cool Features Include:- More than 100 pictures of Pet dog- Multiple difficulty levels (from 3*3 to the most difficult 7*7).- Save to phone album function.- Images gallery and difficulty selection.Fancy JigSaw is suitable for a wide range of audiences, Many different modes and pictures in the game will keep you excited and entertained for a long time.Keywords:puzzle, puzzles,Jigsaw,games,brain fun,funny,dogs,cute dog,entertainment,wallpapers,animal,nature.

reviews.title: Pet dogs
reviews.comment: Love pets. Love puzzles......however, when I open the app to play, the series starts back at one and I have to scroll each time through each one to get to puzzles I haven\'t done yet.  Is it me or my tablet.  Other puzzle apps have a gallery so you can start anywhere.
